00:00:15.630 --> 00:00:18.730
and it's an event I'm
really learning to enjoy.

00:00:18.730 --> 00:00:23.210
Because last year when I came
here, I kept bumping into friends,

00:00:23.210 --> 00:00:27.890
and colleagues, and neighbors,
and people who, you know,

00:00:27.890 --> 00:00:30.560
