00:00:59.450 --> 00:01:00.900
everybody had a favorite book.

00:01:00.900 --> 00:01:04.110
Everybody immediately came up
with a favorite book of his,

00:01:04.110 --> 00:01:06.440
whether it was "The Risk
Pool," from "The Risk Pool"

00:01:06.440 --> 00:01:09.350
to "The Straight Man," to
"Bridge of Sighs," and, of course,

00:01:09.350 --> 00:01:11.830
his latest book, "Everybody's
Fool" is a sequel

00:01:11.830 --> 00:01:14.440
