00:02:02.250 --> 00:02:03.730
I like to think of
you, Richard Russo,

00:02:03.730 --> 00:02:06.650
as the bard of the working class.

00:02:06.650 --> 00:02:09.640
I think you know what it means
to be a working class guy,

00:02:09.640 --> 00:02:13.190
because you grew up in a town that
prosperity had sort of passed by,

00:02:13.190 --> 00:02:16.560
