00:02:16.560 --> 00:02:17.860
Am I saying that right?

00:02:17.860 --> 00:02:19.160
&gt;&gt; That's right.

00:02:19.160 --> 00:02:20.460
&gt;&gt; I'm assuming I am because --

00:02:20.460 --> 00:02:21.760
&gt;&gt; Yep.

00:02:21.760 --> 00:02:23.060
&gt;&gt; They made gloves.

00:02:23.060 --> 00:02:24.360
&gt;&gt; They did, indeed.

00:02:24.360 --> 00:02:25.660 position:56%
&gt;&gt; So, and then -- and then no more.

00:02:25.660 --> 00:02:28.900
