00:02:28.900 --> 00:02:31.730
these sort of -- we pass
through them sometimes on trips,

00:02:31.730 --> 00:02:33.710
and they're kind of gloomy
and depressing looking,

00:02:33.710 --> 00:02:35.180
but you're fascinated by them.

00:02:35.180 --> 00:02:38.690
What keeps bringing you
back to that setting?

00:02:40.230 --> 00:02:44.470
&gt;&gt; Well, I think that, yeah, I am
fascinated by these towns, and,

00:02:44.470 --> 00:02:49.450
you know, I've given Gloversville
half a dozen different names during

00:02:49.450 --> 00:02:51.230
the decades that I've
been writing about it.

00:02:51.230 --> 00:02:55.910
