00:03:16.610 --> 00:03:23.610
When we're young, I think
the world is deeply wonderful

00:03:23.610 --> 00:03:28.830
and deeply mysterious,
and the older we get,

00:03:28.830 --> 00:03:31.020
the less mysterious it becomes,

00:03:31.020 --> 00:03:34.690
because we see things
happen repeatedly.

00:03:34.690 --> 00:03:36.910
And repetition causes us to believe

00:03:36.910 --> 00:03:44.220 position:56%
that the world is not the miraculous
place that it seems like to a child.

00:03:44.220 --> 00:03:48.810
