00:27:01.850 --> 00:27:06.040
&gt;&gt; Sorry. It is Washington,
D.C., after all.

00:27:06.040 --> 00:27:15.260
&gt;&gt; Well, no, I do feel like my
novels, what I've been writing

00:27:15.260 --> 00:27:21.130
about in my novels since, you
know, for a very long time now,

