00:27:33.350 --> 00:27:36.870
I mean, it was all over by
the end of World War II.

00:27:36.870 --> 00:27:40.600
In a way, Gloversville, New
York, I've come to think of it

00:27:40.600 --> 00:27:44.160
as the canary in the coal mine.

00:27:44.160 --> 00:27:50.010
It was happening there then, but
since that time, it has just --

00:27:50.010 --> 00:27:56.490
the story of Gloversville, New York
