years, I kind of had this subject,

00:28:11.970 --> 00:28:15.190
not to myself, but --
let's put it this way.

00:28:15.190 --> 00:28:17.630
The field was not overly crowded.

00:28:17.630 --> 00:28:18.930
&gt;&gt; Right.

00:28:18.930 --> 00:28:23.150
&gt;&gt; And now suddenly, as you
